NOTICE

This project is a derivative of "rust-skills" by ZhangHanDong
(https://github.com/actionbook/rust-skills), used under the MIT License.

The `unsafe-checker` skill's rule set is derived from the Rust Coding
Guidelines (rust-coding-guidelines-zh):
https://github.com/Rust-Coding-Guidelines/rust-coding-guidelines-zh

Enhancement patterns are extracted from publicly available source code of the
respective projects (LanceDB, Apache DataFusion, Zed, Tauri, LakeSail,
turbopuffer/tantivy/hnsw_rs, OpenAI Codex) for educational reference; each is
cited inline at the point of use.
